*******************************************************************************
* Parameters for the simple soil N-balance
*******************************************************************************
* Initial soil nitrogen availability in the top soil (kg N/ha)
* This value is usually derived from field experiments
NAVAILI = 10.

* Background N deposition (kg N/ha/day)
BG_N_SUPPLY = 0.2

* Recovery fraction of applied N fertilizer (-)
N_RECOVERY_FRACTION = 0.7

